        <abstract> 
<p>Enthusiastic about JS’s work on <hi rend="italic">Passiflora</hi> self-incompatibility.</p>  
<p>CD quotes JS on rostellar pollen germination [in "Fertilisation of orchids", <hi rend="italic">Collected papers</hi> 2: 77–8]. H. Crüger attributes it to ants’ carrying stigmatic secretion to pollen.</p> 
            <p>Homomorphic cowslip seedlings are, sadly, showing variation.</p>
        </abstract>
